{"tid":215982,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"和宜合道私家車撞2少女    一死一重傷","createTime":"2017-04-24T18:53:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-04-26T03:08:07.000Z","uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":9,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6db3bf56da5c951a011d5bed9300993f5c2edf93","tid":215982,"uid":58099,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:53:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://static.apple.appledaily.com.hk/images/e-paper/20170425/large/1493050071_ba33.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fstatic.apple.appledaily.com.hk%2Fimages%2Fe-paper%2F20170425%2Flarge%2F1493050071_ba33.jpg&h=75f82703&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n葵涌發生嚴重車禍。昨晚11時許，一對部藍色私家車沿和宜合道行駛，途至運動場對開時，懷疑失控鏟上行人路，撞倒兩名少女，其中一人被捲入車底重創被困。<br />\n<br />\n消防接報趕至，救出困車底的女子，經救護員搶救證實她已明顯死亡，而另一名女子則重傷。警方正調查意外原因，涉案司機報稱胸口不適，須送院治理。"},{"pid":"f95790f6787441dcd0a64827706fad96a1580e73","tid":215982,"uid":45793,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:53:51.000Z","msg":"司機不得好死<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1d0b30cc52d16ed9728c73541a987194170993fa","tid":215982,"uid":55511,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:54:56.000Z","msg":"果頭好多靚女 學生妹 咁就比你車死兩件<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"69152a29361adebba8481b7d0ba2502bbc2367d6","tid":215982,"uid":43510,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T18:57:27.000Z","msg":"明顯死亡<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d6ded90cd4d59e8743c23459a014615cba535a5a","tid":215982,"uid":79390,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-04-24T19:05:22.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"http://hk.on.cc/hk/bkn/cnt/news/20170425/mobile/bkn-20170425014839042-0425_00822_001.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fhk.on.cc%2Fhk%2Fbkn%2Fcnt%2Fnews%2F20170425%2Fmobile%2Fbkn-20170425014839042-0425_00822_001.html&d=lmKMjREij7Lxzb1c6qtKJE%2Fk3Pi4b370HO%2